poc_project.models.RequestLogModel module¶

class poc_project.models.RequestLogModel.RequestLog(*, id: int | None = None, path: str, processing_time: float)[source]¶

Bases: SQLModel

Represents a log entry for a request processed by an application.

id¶

An optional integer field representing the unique identifier of the log entry. It is set as the primary key of the table and can be automatically generated by the database.

Type:

int | None

path¶

A string field representing the path of the request (e.g., “/api/users”).

Type:

str

processing_time¶

A float field representing the time taken to process the request in seconds.

Type:

float

id: int | None¶
